ty)\n\n- **Other highly rated options**:\n  - **Holistique Healing Spa** — 4.9 stars from ~1,175 reviews; broad wellness and aesthetics focus.[[1]](https://www.medicalspalocator.com/city/katy)\n  - **Hibiscus Aesthetics & Wellness**, **Viata Aesthetics and Wellness**, **Luminous MediSpa**, and **Le Chloé Med Spa** — Multiple 4.8–5.0 ratings with solid review counts; good for injectables, weight loss, or boutique experiences.[[4]](https://www.hibiscus.health/)[[5]](https://www.viataaestheticsandwellness.com/)\n  - Yelp frequently lists Medspa at Villagio, SkinSpirit Katy, 4Ever Glow Salon & MedSpa, and Ageless Med Spa among the top 10.[[3]](https://www.yelp.com/search?cflt=medicalspa&find_loc=Katy%2C+TX)\n\n### Tips for Choosing\n- **Check credentials**: Look for board-certified providers or physician oversight, especially for injectables or advanced lasers.\n- **Review volume matters**: Higher numbers (hundreds to 1,000+) give a more reliable picture than a few perfect scores.\n- **Local awards & mentions**: MedSpa at Villagio’s skincare awards and “Best of Katy” category contenders add credibility.\n- **Practical steps**: Read the latest Google/Yelp reviews for your desired service, confirm pricing/specials, and visit for a consultation. Many offer online booking.\n\nRatings can shift, so verify directly on Google, Yelp, or the spas’ sites for the most current info. If you have a specific treatment in mind (e.g., Botox, laser hair removal, or weight loss), provide more details for tailored suggestions!","logprobs":[],"annotations":[{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.medicalspalocator.com/city/katy","start_index":452,"end_index":502,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.medicalspalocator.com/city/katy","start_index":502,"end_index":552,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.medicalspalocator.com/city/katy","start_index":910,"end_index":960,"title":"1"},{"type":"url_citation","url":"https://www.medicalspalocator.com/city/katy",